name: rules
title: SERVER RULES
description:
1 - Please put things in the correct channel it is designated to. (EX; OwO bot goes in <#725539079021920266> )

2 - NSFW is allowed, but keep it in it's channel please. <#725543533175636099>  ("Only for the horny" -noodle. June 24, 2020)

3 - You must be 13+ to be here, if you're not, contact one of the admins and we'll talk about it. (We do not want children to see things they shouldn't be seeing.) 

4 - Admins, do not abuse your power. You have 3 chances, if you keep acting up, you will be banned or possibly lose your admin. 

5 - Do not add bots without permission from me or noodle (for admins)

6 - Do not bully/harass people. this is a friendly community. 

7 - This server is LGBTQ+ friendly, we do not appreciate any hate. you will be punished for this, I understand it's your opinion, but keep it to yourself.

8 - If you have any triggers add them here ----> <#725551866435469423>
